# 3DS Game Creator - by StableDweller2

A visual, block-based game creation tool for the Nintendo New 3DS, inspired by Scratch. 
Built with Electron and vanilla JavaScript — no frameworks required.

## What it does
- Drag and drop code blocks to program sprites and backgrounds
- 117+ blocks across 10 categories including 3DS-exclusive hardware blocks
- Per-sprite and per-background Code, Textures, and Sounds tabs
- Live preview panel with a fully accurate New 3DS shell (working joysticks, sliders, and buttons)
- Save and load projects as .json files with auto-save every 5 minutes
- Export to Nintendo 3DS homebrew via devkitPro (coming soon)

## Built with
- Electron
- Vanilla HTML / CSS / JavaScript
- devkitPro / libctru (planned for export)

## Setup
Make sure you have Node.js installed, then:

    npm install
    npm start

## Status
Early development — block editor, preview, and save/load are functional.
Texture editor, sound editor, and 3DS export are in progress.

## Target platform
Nintendo New 3DS via custom firmware (CFW) and devkitPro homebrew toolchain.